en_US.DialogText: What can I do for you?

zh_CN.DialogText: 咳咳...我们对你非常失望，原本以为你愿意用知识来换取其他人收集的资源。

en_US.DialogText: ahem...We are very disappointed with you. We thought you were willing to exchange knowledge for resources collected by others.

zh_CN.DialogText: 但是你只是索取而全无贡献，今后你无法获取公社的帮助了，无论是药品还是食物

en_US.DialogText: But you only ask for but have no contribution. In the future, you can't get the help of the commune, whether it's medicine or food

zh_CN.DialogText: 别担心，我们不会孤立你的，要是你愿意用什么东西来交易，那也是可以的。

en_US.DialogText: Don't worry, we won't isolate you. If you're willing to trade something, it's OK.

zh_CN.DialogText: 他们走了......在末日里独善其身或许是不错的选择......

en_US.DialogText: They're gone.... It may be a good choice to be alone at the end of the day....

zh_CN.DialogText: 但是或许人们要像远古冰期的人类一样团结在一起，才能生存下来......

en_US.DialogText: But maybe people have to unite like humans in the ancient ice age in order to survive
